Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Unsporting manners
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03zjmk0
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 3 Oct 1976
Unsporting manners. Violence erupts outside Yankee Stadium as police go on strike. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.